resources.string: Hey! We are so glad you are loving our app. We would love your feedback so it can help us make a great choice.
Let\'s set up your child\'s profile.
Your child\'s name has been set.

Personal information is any information that identifies a user as an individual

We do not collect any personal information from children in our mobile apps or on our website.

We may collect personal from parents and teachers when they voluntarily provide it. This may include collecting email addresses when parents and teachers sign up.

If you submit a feedback, we may need your email address and other information you provide related to your support request. We use this information to provide only support to you. We don't share your email address unless we have your express consent.

This app don't use or collect a user's precise geographic location.
This app don't contain any advertising banners.
This app may contain external links to our page on the Play Store or to our Facebook page but it is all kept in the parent section where young kids can't access.

If you have any questions regarding to this Disclaimer, please send us an email to: arabelle.mon@lorma.edu
This device doesn\'t support Camera2 API.
